juanyuk.photoalbum.model

Class Album

  • java.lang.Object
    • juanyuk.photoalbum.model.Album
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Album>, java.util.Comparator<Album>

    public class Album
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Album>, java.util.Comparator<Album>, java.io.Serializable
    Class representation of a photo album. Album will have a collection of photos with the ability to create and remove photos.
    Author:
    yuky, jmm754
